Text: The secret is out! After 5 years in NYC, I am officially back in the city that raised me, ATL. Today I bought  my first home, my dream townhome! A huge thank you to my friends, family, amazing realtor, and Twitter for supporting me through this process. I’m back y’all!

3 years at Twitter today! Through all the crazy of the past year, Twitter (and team cpg) has been a stable home and I am forever grateful. So proud to be a tweep, today and everyday. #LoveTwitter #LoveWhereYouWork and missing you all IRL
HAPPY 3 YEARS TO MY PIC  Beyond grateful for you.
